<paragraph blockId="15.[1466,2677,299,2061]" pageId="15" pageNumber="122">
<taxonomicName authority="Nelson, 1904" authorityName="Nelson" authorityYear="1904" box="[1472,1833,379,404]" class="Mammalia" family="Leporidae" genus="Sylvilagus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lagomorpha" pageId="15" pageNumber="122" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="cunicularius" subSpecies="pacificus">S. c. pacificus Nelson, 1904</taxonomicName>
— S Michoacan, Guerrero (except the N &amp; NE), and SW tip of Oaxaca (S Mexico).
